race.description: Mangrove Mountain Club & Golf Course Town Mdn Plate
race.comment: Good maiden with plenty of chances. SEQUISTA (11) bumped into some smart types in both preps and resumes in a winnable contest. Wasn't pushed out in her two trials and will take catching from the barrier. COMPOSED (1) progressive colt looking for this trip at his third career start. Produced good closing splits when a respectable second over 1000m at Hawkesbury. Gets his chance. OPETAIA (9) Deep Field filly out of Forest Fantasy on debut for the Baker stable. All four trials had merit and stays in the calculations. GLORIA (8) Maurice filly on debut for the Waugh yard. Ticks a few boxes and worth thought.
